 href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"967be79d5edaeba6b78ed1d32915ff4afea3a9cd","tid":1467632,"uid":241458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"聽日停止捉鬼，和理非式舉牌話今晚單嘢係衝動咗，低低地摜一鋪，坐返喺接機大堂，沖淡返今日啲嘢先"}]}